reviewText: This is absolutely one of the very best movies I have ever seen.  I ordered it and have watched it four times in a row.  It is the Real Thing.
This is such a great film with a lot for my kids to think about.  Glad to have found it.

This is probably the best movie to come along in the last few years.  The movie told a story of life.  It told a story of pain, hurt, love and adversity.  Buy this movie and I can assure you you'll be glad you did.
A touching tell of a women struggling and a man trying to get passed his passed. This is an antiabortion movie that is comprehensible and thoughtful.
